    </h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1 text-sm">SoliDB</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Built-in document database, queried with AQL.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1 text-sm">Active-Record-style Model API</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400"><code class="text-emerald-300">find</code>, <code class="text-emerald-300">where</code>, <code class="text-emerald-300">order</code>, <code class="text-emerald-300">create</code>, <code class="text-emerald-300">update</code>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1 text-sm">Relationships</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400"><code class="text-emerald-300">belongs_to</code>, <code class="text-emerald-300">has_many</code>, has-and-belongs-to-many.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
