            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1 text-sm">Auth &amp; security</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">JWT auth, policy-based authorization, CSRF, XSS sanitization, Argon2, secure cookies.</p>
        </div>
