        Developer Tools
    </h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1 text-sm">Hot reload</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Edit and refresh &mdash; no restart needed.</p>
